title: Railworks TS2014 DT BR Class 4MT 4-6-0 Tender Loco
description:
BR Class 4MT 4-6-0 Tender Loco.

Pack Features:

- Custom Cab and Sounds
- Quick Drives
- Accurate Physics
- Light Effects
- Working Headcode system changeable on the fly
- TS2013 compatible



Please support the developers and buy some of their content if you can afford it.


Please use the email address or the facebook fanpage for requests, questions and 

also if you want to share an addon with the community which we will post on your 

behalf.

If you would like to contribute, please read the Readme.pdf.
